==Form event types==

This is the application of event types, with it you can add, modify and view all data on the event type classified in different tabs: main data, data on the registry modifications and assignments to folders.

===Data Tab event type===

In this tab you can view and modify the main details of the event type. Here we relate all information fields.

[tiposevento-formulario.png]

- **Name (*):** Name the type of event.
- **Description:** Description of the type of event.


(*) **Required when creating or modifying a form of payment Campos.**

